{"id":2933,"date":"2019-09-14T05:08:47","date_gmt":"2019-09-14T05:08:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=2933"},"modified":"2019-12-31T10:40:53","modified_gmt":"2019-12-31T03:40:53","slug":"cach-thiet-ke-to-roi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#Chon_lua_mau_sac_su_dung\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\">Ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#Noi_bat_thuong_hieu_doanh_nghiep\" title=\"N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p\">N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#Su_dung_hinh_anh_linh_hoat\" title=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh linh ho\u1ea1t\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh linh ho\u1ea1t<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#Noi_dung_muon_the_hien_ngan_gon_xuc_tich\" title=\"N\u1ed9i dung mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, x\u00fac t\u00edch\">N\u1ed9i dung mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, x\u00fac t\u00edch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#CTA_cua_to_roi_hap_dan\" title=\"CTA c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn\">CTA c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/#Hinh_dang_kich_co_cua_to_roi\" title=\"H\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng, k\u00edch c\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i\">H\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng, k\u00edch c\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng tin qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n <strong>c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p <\/strong>chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chon_lua_mau_sac_su_dung\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Tuy v\u1eady thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, ng\u00e0nh kinh doanh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1ec7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2931\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2931\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2931 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o.jpg\" alt=\"l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i\" width=\"825\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o.jpg 825w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-300x167.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/vai-tr\u00f2-c\u1ee7a-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-768x428.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2931\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i xem x\u00e9t k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0o s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 m\u00e0u xanh l\u00e1 v\u00e0 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c tone m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1ebb em. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u00f4ng t\u1edd r\u01a1i th\u1eadt s\u1eb7c s\u1ee1, hay ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3 th\u1eadt \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eddi t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 m\u00e0u? Nh\u00ecn t\u1edd r\u01a1i ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi hai m\u00e0u \u0111en tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? (c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p).<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/vai-tro-to-roi-quang-cao.html\/\">Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Noi_bat_thuong_hieu_doanh_nghiep\"><\/span><strong>N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p b\u1ea1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean t\u1edd r\u01a1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem bi\u1ebft n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ai. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 g\u00ec thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u1ea7n: Logo, tagline, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 website? Th\u1ebf c\u00f2n ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3u ch\u1eef ri\u00eang ch\u1ee9? Doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u1eb7c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0o m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn ra kh\u00f4ng?<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2934\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2934\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2934\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/th\u01b0\u01a1ng-hi\u1ec7u-c\u00f4ng-ty-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i.jpg\" alt=\"thiet ke to roi\" width=\"825\" height=\"609\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/th\u01b0\u01a1ng-hi\u1ec7u-c\u00f4ng-ty-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i.jpg 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/th\u01b0\u01a1ng-hi\u1ec7u-c\u00f4ng-ty-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-300x222.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/th\u01b0\u01a1ng-hi\u1ec7u-c\u00f4ng-ty-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-t\u1edd-r\u01a1i-768x567.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2934\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00f4ng ty n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_dung_hinh_anh_linh_hoat\"><\/span><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh linh ho\u1ea1t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1\u00a0h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn? S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda, minh h\u1ecda, icon ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ho\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tranh v\u1ebd n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf b\u00ean tr\u00ean, h\u00e3y suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1\u00a0th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Noi_dung_muon_the_hien_ngan_gon_xuc_tich\"><\/span><strong>N\u1ed9i dung mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, x\u00fac t\u00edch<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean t\u1edd r\u01a1i. Nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u00ean ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Ti\u1ebfp theo, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp ch\u00fang m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd tr\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1eebng c\u1ed1 nh\u1ed3i nh\u00e9t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin, b\u1edfi c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u00e0ng b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2935\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/n\u1ed9i-dung-n\u00ean-h\u1ebft-s\u1ee9c-ng\u1eafn-g\u1ecdn.png\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p\" width=\"825\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/n\u1ed9i-dung-n\u00ean-h\u1ebft-s\u1ee9c-ng\u1eafn-g\u1ecdn.png 1206w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/n\u1ed9i-dung-n\u00ean-h\u1ebft-s\u1ee9c-ng\u1eafn-g\u1ecdn-300x179.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/n\u1ed9i-dung-n\u00ean-h\u1ebft-s\u1ee9c-ng\u1eafn-g\u1ecdn-768x459.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/n\u1ed9i-dung-n\u00ean-h\u1ebft-s\u1ee9c-ng\u1eafn-g\u1ecdn-1024x611.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CTA_cua_to_roi_hap_dan\"><\/span><strong>CTA c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem l\u00e0m sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc qua t\u1edd r\u01a1i, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u00ec &#8211; \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 trang social c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link website \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, hay nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa. H\u00e3y l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u CTA th\u1eadt \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111o\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2936\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2936\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2936\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/CTA-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-c\u1ea7n-l\u00f4i-cu\u1ed1n.png\" alt=\"CTA\" width=\"825\" height=\"1190\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/CTA-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-c\u1ea7n-l\u00f4i-cu\u1ed1n.png 500w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/CTA-v\u1edbi-n\u1ed9i-dung-c\u1ea7n-l\u00f4i-cu\u1ed1n-208x300.png 208w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2936\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">CTA v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ea7n l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hinh_dang_kich_co_cua_to_roi\"><\/span><strong>H\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng, k\u00edch c\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u1edd r\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng kh\u1ed5 A5. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef k\u00edch c\u1ee1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, hay mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t?<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc kh\u1ed5 to h\u01a1n cho t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o g\u00ec trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi c\u1ea7m, n\u1eafm, \u0111\u1ecdc, g\u1ea5p t\u1edd r\u01a1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng?<\/p>\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p m\u00e0 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media chia s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea1n. Mong r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n trong vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-to-roi.html\/\"> <strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/strong><\/a>,<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-web-la-gi-dich-vu-thiet-ke-website-gia-re-tai-ha-noi.html\/\"> <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/strong><\/a> v\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/giai-phap-thuong-hieu\/\"><strong>nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p marketing<\/strong><\/a> cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p&#8230; Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng tin qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. B\u00e0i v